581
00:57:40.161 --> 00:57:41.128
Don't.

582
00:57:42.461 --> 00:57:44.164
Time for a better view.

583
00:57:48.235 --> 00:57:50.003
Energy level's stable. and...

584
00:57:50.137 --> 00:57:52.039
