598
00:58:25.005 --> 00:58:27.307
He's so good. I used some
of his open-source code

599
00:58:27.440 --> 00:58:30.543
- in this program.
- Wait. you used open-source code

600
00:58:30.677 --> 00:58:32.646
in my billion-dollar prototype?

601
