616
00:59:12.485 --> 00:59:14.387
Left lung is collapsing.

617
00:59:15.556 --> 00:59:17.391
Heart rate's at 143.

618
00:59:22.730 --> 00:59:24.264
Look. mate.
there's a laundry list

619
00:59:24.398 --> 00:59:26.766
